snippet.title: Version 2.2 "Into the Perilous Labyrinth of Fog" Trailer | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
The trials of the warriors are hidden in the domain, the sorrowful past buried in the hazy fog.
When the veil of mystery is lifted, regardless if you are a martial artist craving for combat
or a Traveler from a distant land, all will be revealed.
